Package: geoloctools
Type: Package
Title: A Geolocation Tracking Toolbox
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(person(
               family = "Hufkens",
               given = "Koen",
               email = "koen.hufkens@gmail.com",
               role = c("aut", "cre"),
               comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5070-8109")),
            person(given = "BlueGreen Labs",
              role = c("cph", "fnd"))
           )
Description: A set of functions to pre-process geolocation tracking data. This
  includes both light loggers, GPS loggers of all kinds, and tries to ensure
  interoperability between various devices and formats for synthesis and
  analysis.
URL: https://github.com/bluegreen-labs/geoloctools
BugReports: https://github.com/bluegreen-labs/geoloctools/issues
